<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Lingolandias</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #9c27b0;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-top-left-radius: 8px;
      border-top-right-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .content a {
      color: #3a8dff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }

    /* Responsive Styles */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        padding: 15px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Lingolandias!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>We're excited to have you join us at Lingolandias! Here are your login details:</p>
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
      <p><strong>Password:</strong> <%= password %></p>
      <p>You can log in to your account at <a href="https://lingolandias.com">lingolandias.com</a>.</p>
      <p>We hope you enjoy your experience with us!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Lingolandias. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
